---
---

<section id="robots" class="robots-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2>How It Works</h2>
      <p>Three steps. Your voice in, review-ready content out.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="robots-grid">
      <div class="robot-card">
        <div class="step-number">1</div>
        <div class="robot-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Feed Your Voice</h3>
          <div class="robot-icon card-title-icon">🧠</div>
        </div>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Weekly Ritual + Personas</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Complete a 5-minute weekly ritual</li>
          <li>Define your audience personas</li>
          <li>AI suggestions use your voice, tone, and positioning</li>
          <li>Your narrative arc evolves over time</li>
          <li>You keep the final say before anything goes out</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="robot-card featured">
        <div class="featured-badge">The Workflow</div>
        <div class="robot-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>AI Drafts Content</h3>
          <div class="robot-icon card-title-icon">⚡</div>
        </div>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Multiple Formats, One Pipeline</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Content angles matched to your audience's problems</li>
          <li>Articles, newsletters, social posts, shorts</li>
          <li>Real keyword data drives every piece</li>
          <li>Affiliate opportunities surfaced when they match</li>
          <li>Scheduling stays visible before publish</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="robot-card">
        <div class="step-number">3</div>
        <div class="robot-card-header card-title-row">
          <h3>Review & Approve</h3>
          <div class="robot-icon card-title-icon">👆</div>
        </div>
        <p class="robot-tagline">Review in Seconds</p>
        <ul class="robot-features">
          <li>Open the app on your phone</li>
          <li>Approve, skip, or edit before publishing</li>
          <li>Edit inline if needed</li>
          <li>Publish through supported connected channels</li>
          <li>Track performance in analytics</li>
          <li>If the backend is offline, supported edits are queued and retried</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .robots-section {
        padding: var(--space-24) 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--color-surface) 0%, var(--color-surface-subtle) 100%);
  }

  .robots-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(calc(var(--space-20) * 3.75), 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-8);
    margin-top: var(--space-12);
  }

  .robot-card {
    background: var(--color-surface);
    padding: var(--space-10);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    transition: box-shadow var(--duration-slow), transform var(--duration-slow);
    position: relative;
  }

  .robot-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(var(--motion-lift-card));
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card-lg);
  }

  .robot-card.featured {
    border: calc(var(--space-1) * 0.75) solid var(--color-primary);
    transform: scale(var(--card-featured-scale));
  }

  .step-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(var(--space-4) * -1);
    left: var(--space-5);
    width: var(--space-10);
    height: var(--space-10);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: var(--text-base);
  }

  .featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(var(--space-4) * -1);
    right: var(--space-5);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-secondary));
    color: var(--color-text-on-dark);
        padding: var(--space-2) var(--space-4);
    border-radius: var(--radius-xl);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .robot-card-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .robot-icon {
    display: inline-flex;
    width: calc(var(--space-8) + var(--space-1));
    height: calc(var(--space-8) + var(--space-1));
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-pill);
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface-card-glass) 82%, transparent);
    box-shadow: inset 0 0 var(--space-1) color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-white) 24%, transparent);
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .robot-icon {
      animation: emoji-bounce 4.2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .robot-card:nth-child(1) .robot-icon {
      animation-delay: 0.15s;
    }

    .robot-card:nth-child(2) .robot-icon {
      animation-delay: 0.55s;
    }

    .robot-card:nth-child(3) .robot-icon {
      animation-delay: 0.95s;
    }
  }

  @keyframes emoji-bounce {
    0%,
    100% {
      transform: translateY(0) rotate(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: translateY(calc(var(--space-1) * -0.5)) rotate(-6deg);
    }
  }

  .robot-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-h3);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .robot-tagline {
    color: var(--color-primary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-6);
  }

  .robot-features {
    list-style: none;
  }

  .robot-features li {
        padding: var(--space-2) 0;
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
    border-bottom: calc(var(--space-1) / 4) solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .robot-features li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .robot-features li::before {
    content: "\2192  ";
    color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .robots-section {
            padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    }

    .robots-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-8);
      margin-top: var(--space-8);
    }

    .robot-card {
            padding: var(--space-6) var(--space-6) var(--space-6);
    }

    .robot-card.featured {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }
</style>
